    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《DEADSIDE》将众多广受喜爱的生存射击游戏的元素融合在了一个快节奏的开放世界之中。玩家能够快速发展，获取丰厚的战利品。你可以获得珍贵装备并将其存放在安全区内，也可以在荒野中打造自己的坚固堡垒——用炮塔来建立防卫，将其打造成提供属性加成的舒适居所，还可以用来存放你的载具和战利品。在游戏世界中可以徒步、驾车、骑行、划船，或是用地铁系统来快速旅行。你可以广交朋友，也可以四处树敌。选择加入PVP或PVE服务器，探索充满挑战的广阔世界，并对你的敌人发起突袭。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/ffaeaef629d0c86c5fc944350d4ac914.poster.avif?t=1770224095\" width=668 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/ffaeaef629d0c86c5fc944350d4ac914.webm?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/ffaeaef629d0c86c5fc944350d4ac914.mp4?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PVP、PVE与突袭</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《DEADSIDE》1.0版本中，我们有三种服务器供你选择：PVP、PVE与PVP不清档服务器。<i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PVP服务器为玩家提供激烈的硬核体验，玩家可以自由对战，也可以毫无限制地突袭掠夺他人的基地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PVE服务器则提供更为休闲的游戏体验，玩家间可以和平互动，无法互相攻击或突袭/掠夺他人基地。我们推荐使用此模式来熟悉游戏机制。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PVP不清档服务器则是二者混合，允许玩家对战，但无法突袭基地。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >基地建设与舒适度系统</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/eb9f177d0943d3468479f5d12f58311d.poster.avif?t=1770224095\" width=668 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/eb9f177d0943d3468479f5d12f58311d.webm?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/eb9f177d0943d3468479f5d12f58311d.mp4?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建造隐蔽的小屋或防御森严的堡垒。我们提供直观易用的工具来让建造变得轻松便捷，还加入了大量能提供游戏加成的舒适物品。使用炮塔和陷阱等被动防御设施保护基地。存放你的载具，并保护你辛苦赢来的战利品免遭突袭掠夺。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >载具与快速旅行</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/0174e6f4d5c5c71d902e291c0c3419e0.poster.avif?t=1770224095\" width=668 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/0174e6f4d5c5c71d902e291c0c3419e0.webm?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/0174e6f4d5c5c71d902e291c0c3419e0.mp4?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在开放世界生存游戏中，没人喜欢永无休止的长跑。《DEADSIDE》提供船只、摩托车、汽车和快速传送系统以便于探索地图。用密码锁保护你的载具，载具还能用作储物空间。 </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《DEADSIDE》的世界 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/079360c616e07acb720434ad253027c6.poster.avif?t=1770224095\" width=668 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/079360c616e07acb720434ad253027c6.webm?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/079360c616e07acb720434ad253027c6.mp4?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索这片后苏联末世中的森林、河流和定居点。你可以在定居点外任意建造。具有挑战性的NPC在地图上四处巡逻，而你的成长完全取决于个人技术。这里没有等级或进度条，你的“等级”就体现在你的技术和你获得的装备之上。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >武器与战斗系统 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/5d3d4e6718ad8922d88c54f10613e6d4.poster.avif?t=1770224095\" width=668 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/5d3d4e6718ad8922d88c54f10613e6d4.webm?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/895400/extras/5d3d4e6718ad8922d88c54f10613e6d4.mp4?t=1770224095\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 精确的弹道系统，丰富多样的武器。32种枪械任你选择，可搭配瞄准镜、扩容弹匣、手电筒、消音器等多种模块。喜欢玩战术？设置绊线陷阱，部署重生点，用烟雾弹作掩护。战斗系统专为硬核玩家而打造。《DEADSIDE》拥有直观的任务系统，会在地图上清晰地标记出PVE事件。</p>",
